										<span><a href="javascript:;" onclick="spgCommon.bindDownloadDataFromEl(&quot;10.11648.j.ajcst.20250801.13.bib&quot;, &#39;.bib-copy-pop-src&#39;)"><img src="/img/download_icon.png">Download</a></span>
									</p>
